*Edward Acheson (British Army officer) (1844–1921), English cricketer and British Army officer</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q900982" start="31" end="54" title="Edward Goodrich Acheson" label="Edward Goodrich Acheson"/>
<link wikidata="Q19661092" start="86" end="108" title="Edward Campion Acheson" label="Edward Campion Acheson"/>
