* &quot;Sanford and Son&quot; (1972–77) – Grady Wilson
* &quot;Grady&quot; (1975–76) – Grady Wilson
* &quot;That&#x27;s Cat&quot; (1976) – Grandpa
* &quot;Baretta&quot; (1976) – Joey Rich
* &quot;Sesame Street&quot; (1976–1977)
* &quot;Sanford Arms&quot; (1977) – Grady Wilson
* &quot;Starsky and Hutch&quot; (1978) – Jeeter
